title: For Sale:  COP 4 BARREL 357/38 SPEC.
postcontent: The COP 357 is an extremely rare pistol that is no longer in production. Made famous in the movie "Blade Runner" and seen in such movies as "Bad Boys", "The Matrix Reloaded",and most recently "21 Jump Street" the COP would be a welcomed piece to any collectors collection, Or just for anyone looking for something rare, beautiful, and different. Easy to fire and easy on the eyes this rare pistol has 4 barrels which fire 357 magnums or .38 specials. The COP 357 is a 4 shot Derringer type pistol chambered for the powerful .357 Magnum round. It was designed by Robert Hillberg, based on his earlier work on the Hillberg Insurgency Weapon. It was manufactured by the now defunct COP Inc. of 3040 West Lomita Blvd., Torrance, California (COP stood for Compact Off-Duty Police). The double action weapon is about twice as wide, and substantially heavier than the typical .25 automatic pistol, though its relatively compact size and powerful cartridge made it a good choice for a defensive weapon or a police backup gun. The COP 357 is quite robust in design and construction. It is made of solid stainless steel components. Cartridges are loaded into the four separate chambers by sliding a latch that "pops-up" the barrel for loading purposes, similar to top-break shotguns. Each of the four chambers has its own dedicated firing pin. It uses an internal hammer, which is activated by depressing the trigger to hit a ratcheting/rotating striker that in turn strikes one firing pin at a time, which is completely internal, to fire each chamber in sequence. Any questions please feel free to email me[will ship to dealer after payment. payment usps money order only] you pay all fees--dealer  and shipping.FIRM  has org case,and owners hand book .has ivory grips carved ,it is mint.has org. grips i have 2 of these. both carved grips and both have there org. cases.[ ONECASE IS RUFF FROM BEING IN GLOVE BOX also THE ORQ.MANUEL IS A REPRINT ON THE RUFF ONE ]  have org. bill of sale on this one. bought in 10/3/80,pck up at a dealer in my area or can ship fed x.to a dealer in your area.buyer pays all fees and shipping.have dealer contact me .NOTICE THIS IS NOT A SCAM .1ST TIME SELLING ON HERE ,MY NEED HELP TO COMPLETE TRANS.
